3. Never ever drink Tea 
Why? because cha pivathi mane kai energy nathi malti ke hu aakho divas energetic feel nathi karto , mane nakri ungh j aavya kare chhe , means e cafine mari enrergy spike nathi kari shaktu and cafine ne lidhe mane nakru stress and depression karan vagar nu feel thaya rakhe chhe
jyarthi cha-cofee pivanu bandh karyu chhe tyarthi ketlu badhu kaam baaki hoy chhe pan dimaag mathi stress , tanav , chinta saav udi j gai chhe
